nl.vumc.trait.oc.connect
Class OCConnector

java.lang.Object
  nl.vumc.trait.oc.connect.OCConnector
Direct Known Subclasses:
OCWebServices
public class OCConnector
extends java.lang.Object

Supports "low-level" interaction with OpenClinica web services such as exception handling, credentials and soap handler setup.

Author:
Arjan van der Velde (ag.vandervelde@vumc.nl)
